flowchart TD
    U[User goal] --> C[Collect context]
    C --> P[Plan next step]
    P --> T{Need a tool?}
    T -- no --> R[Respond]
    T -- yes --> A[Request or use tool]
    A --> O[Observe result]
    O --> V{Goal met?}
    V -- no --> C
    V -- yes --> R
    O --> I{Untrusted content?}
    I -- yes --> G[Apply guardrails]
    G --> P
